---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "2024-12-19";
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Cookie Policy - Martin Carrasco" 
  description="Cookie Policy for Martin Carrasco's portfolio website. Learn about the cookies we use and how to manage your preferences."
  image="https://pub-55f502b1bb8a47b18e001af1f25c9d6c.r2.dev/profile-picture.jpeg"
  tags={["cookie policy", "cookies", "privacy", "GDPR", "legal"]}
  canonicalURL="https://www.martiixx.dev/cookie-policy"
>
  <section class="policy-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
        <p>
          Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device (computer, tablet, or mobile phone) when you visit a website. They are widely used to make websites work more efficiently and provide information to website owners.
        </p>

        <h2>2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use cookies for several purposes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for the website to function properly</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Help us understand how visitors use our website</li>
          <li><strong>Performance Cookies:</strong> Monitor website performance and identify issues</li>
          <li><strong>Preference Cookies:</strong> Remember your cookie consent choices</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>

        <h3>3.1 Essential Cookies</h3>
        <div class="cookie-table">
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Cookie Name</th>
                <th>Purpose</th>
                <th>Duration</th>
                <th>Type</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>analytics-consent</td>
                <td>Stores your consent for analytics cookies</td>
                <td>365 days</td>
                <td>Preference</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>performance-consent</td>
                <td>Stores your consent for performance cookies</td>
                <td>365 days</td>
                <td>Preference</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>cookie-preferences</td>
                <td>Stores your overall cookie preferences</td>
                <td>365 days</td>
                <td>Preference</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h3>3.2 Analytics Cookies (Google Analytics 4)</h3>
        <p>We use Google Analytics 4 to understand how visitors interact with our website. These cookies help us:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Analyze website traffic and usage patterns</li>
          <li>Understand which pages are most popular</li>
          <li>Identify areas for improvement</li>
          <li>Measure the effectiveness of our content</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="cookie-table">
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Cookie Name</th>
                <th>Purpose</th>
                <th>Duration</th>
                <th>Type</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>_ga</td>
                <td>Distinguishes unique users</td>
                <td>2 years</td>
                <td>Analytics</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>_ga_[CONTAINER_ID]</td>
                <td>Persists session state</td>
                <td>2 years</td>
                <td>Analytics</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>_gid</td>
                <td>Distinguishes users for 24 hours</td>
                <td>24 hours</td>
                <td>Analytics</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h3>3.3 Performance Cookies</h3>
        <p>These cookies help us monitor website performance and identify technical issues:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Track Core Web Vitals (LCP, FID, CLS)</li>
          <li>Monitor page load times</li>
          <li>Identify slow-loading resources</li>
          <li>Track JavaScript errors</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services that may set their own cookies:</p>

        <h3>4.1 Google Analytics</h3>
        <p>Google Analytics is a web analytics service provided by Google. It uses cookies to help us analyze how users use our website. The information generated by these cookies about your use of our website (including your IP address) will be transmitted to and stored by Google on servers in the United States.</p>
        <p><strong>Google Analytics Privacy Policy:</strong> <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://policies.google.com/privacy</a></p>

        <h2>5. Your Cookie Choices</h2>
        <p>You have several options for managing cookies:</p>

        <h3>5.1 Cookie Consent Management</h3>
        <p>When you first visit our website, you'll see a cookie consent banner that allows you to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Accept All Cookies:</strong> Enable all analytics and performance cookies</li>
          <li><strong>Decline All Cookies:</strong> Disable all non-essential cookies</li>
          <li><strong>Custom Preferences:</strong> Choose which specific cookie types to enable</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>5.2 Browser Settings</h3>
        <p>You can also control cookies through your browser settings:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Chrome:</strong> Settings ‚Üí Privacy and security ‚Üí Cookies and other site data</li>
          <li><strong>Firefox:</strong> Options ‚Üí Privacy & Security ‚Üí Cookies and Site Data</li>
          <li><strong>Safari:</strong> Preferences ‚Üí Privacy ‚Üí Manage Website Data</li>
          <li><strong>Edge:</strong> Settings ‚Üí Cookies and site permissions ‚Üí Cookies and site data</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>5.3 Google Analytics Opt-out</h3>
        <p>To opt out of Google Analytics tracking, you can:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use the Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on</li>
          <li>Decline analytics cookies through our consent banner</li>
          <li>Use browser settings to block third-party cookies</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Impact of Disabling Cookies</h2>
        <p>If you choose to disable certain cookies, please be aware that:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Essential cookies</strong> cannot be disabled as they are required for basic website functionality</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong> help us improve our website - disabling them may affect our ability to provide the best user experience</li>
          <li><strong>Performance cookies</strong> help us identify and fix technical issues - disabling them may prevent us from detecting problems</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Cookie Consent and GDPR</h2>
        <p>If you are located in the European Economic Area (EEA), we comply with GDPR requirements:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Explicit Consent:</strong> We only set non-essential cookies after obtaining your explicit consent</li>
          <li><strong>Granular Control:</strong> You can choose which specific types of cookies to accept</li>
          <li><strong>Easy Withdrawal:</strong> You can change your cookie preferences at any time</li>
          <li><strong>Clear Information:</strong> We provide transparent information about what each cookie does</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>8. Updates to This Cookie Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the new Cookie Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.</p>

        <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about our use of cookies or this Cookie Policy, please contact us:</p>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:martingodoycarrasco@gmail.com">martingodoycarrasco@gmail.com</a></p>
          <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://www.martiixx.dev">www.martiixx.dev</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="cookie-management">
          <h3>Manage Your Cookie Preferences</h3>
          <p>You can update your cookie preferences at any time by clicking the button below:</p>
          <button onclick="showCookiePreferences()" class="manage-cookies-btn">
            üç™ Manage Cookie Preferences
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-footer">
          <p><strong>Note:</strong> This Cookie Policy is effective as of {lastUpdated} and applies to all users of our website.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .policy-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--background-color) 0%, #1a202c 100%);
    padding: 3rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .policy-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: var(--muted-text);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .policy-content {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: var(--background-color);
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .content-wrapper h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .content-wrapper h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem 0;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .content-wrapper p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--muted-text);
  }

  .content-wrapper ul {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .content-wrapper li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--muted-text);
  }

  .content-wrapper a {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .content-wrapper a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .cookie-table {
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .cookie-table table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    background: #1a202c;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cookie-table th {
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .cookie-table td {
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2d3748;
    color: var(--muted-text);
  }

  .cookie-table tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .contact-info {
    background: #1a202c;
    border: 1px solid #2d3748;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-info a {
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .cookie-management {
    background: rgba(242, 53, 81, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(242, 53, 81, 0.3);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cookie-management h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .manage-cookies-btn {
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .manage-cookies-btn:hover {
    background: #d32f2f;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .policy-footer {
    background: rgba(242, 53, 81, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(242, 53, 81, 0.3);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .policy-footer p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .policy-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .content-wrapper h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .content-wrapper h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .cookie-table {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .cookie-table th,
    .cookie-table td {
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style> 